OL,4,Csport services from charity
OL,6,FAt a meeting on 27 July 2024, elected
OL,7,Fmembers decided that the Active
OL,8,FSchools and sports development
OL,9,Fservices will return under council
OL,10,Fcontrol.
OL,12,FA further report in September will
OL,13,Flook at the future of cultural
OL,14,Ffacilities like libraries, museums,
OL,15,Fand visitor attractions.
OL,17,FThe return of all services to the
OL,18,Fcouncil was also considered.
