OL,6,FAlison Moore, chair of Live Borders,
OL,7,Fadded: "I and my fellow Trustees
OL,8,Faccept today's decision by elected
OL,9,Fmembers to seek to change the
OL,10,Fgovernance of Live Borders
OL,12,F"We will work with Council colleagues
OL,13,Fto ensure that this transition is
OL,14,Forderly and takes place as quickly as
OL,15,Fpossible.
OL,17,F"The Trust remains firmly committed to
OL,18,Fdelivering on our vision of supporting
OL,19,Fa healthier, happier and stronger
OL,20,FScottish Borders."
