OL,3,CCouncil takes back control of some
OL,4,Csport services from charity
OL,6,FLive Borders has been operating since
OL,7,F2016 but in the last few years has
OL,8,Fexperienced financial issues, relying
OL,9,Fon handouts from SBC to keep it afloat.
OL,11,FThe charity has faced unprecedented
OL,12,Fchallenges, including the Covid
OL,13,Fpandemic, cost of living and changes
OL,14,Fin customer trends.
OL,16,FThe charity says it has invested
OL,17,Fmillions of pounds from its financial
OL,18,Freserves into sustaining services,
OL,19,Ffacilities and equipment.
