OL,4,Csport services from charity
OL,6,FThey have also recieved millions of
OL,7,Fpounds of funding from the Council to
OL,8,Fkeep services running.
OL,10,FDavid Robertson, Chief Executive of
OL,11,FScottish Borders Council, said: "It
OL,12,Fwas clear prior to the joint review
OL,13,Fthat changes were required to help
OL,14,FLive Borders get on a sustainable
OL,15,Ffooting and protect the continued
OL,16,Fdelivery of key services to our
OL,17,Fresidents and visitors.
