OL,6,F"We are committed to working closely
OL,7,Fwith the Live Borders board and our
OL,8,Fcolleagues to ensure a seamless
OL,9,Ftransition to the new operating model.
OL,11,F"We will continue to work with Live
OL,12,FBorders on the joint transformational
OL,13,Fchange programme to ensure that
OL,14,Ftogether we are able to deliver the
OL,15,Fchanges that are essential to us being
OL,16,Fable to meet the needs of our
OL,17,Fcommunities in an affordable and
OL,18,Fsustainable way across all sport,
OL,19,Fleisure and culture services."
